{"tid":1611564,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大家可唔可以唔好掉走啲彈","createTime":"2019-10-02T03:53:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-02T06:10:18.000Z","uid":137009,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"746aeea4ed8655809a66a7354723a486a9f81000","tid":1611564,"uid":137009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T03:53:02.000Z","msg":"人地滅煙隊揹住袋水追住啲煙, 跑到過去你一手掉去後面, 其實後面仲有手足走緊<br />\n我唔怪你掉走佢<br />\n但係下次唔好啦<br />\n處理煙有2個方法<br />\n1. 掉入水源<br />\n2. 蓋住佢<br />\n<br />\n掉走佢唔係一個好方法<br />\n因為啲煙會繼續飄出嚟, 對家有專業豬咀, 你掉過去都冇用, 反而滅煙隊會做唔到野"},{"pid":"ac9e80f7b61f403333c89c0f49b0122e81af0e63","tid":1611564,"uid":137009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T04:01:48.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4a440b8acd7e07c27bb8f4fc2d8b9c815eef8e4d","tid":1611564,"uid":186142,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T04:02:30.000Z","msg":"唔好意思 阻阻你<br />\n唔好再指責所謂偽勇武 入嚟睇下小勇武點可以有大作為<br />\n【實際行動戰術整合】正式宣佈下回合開始將會冇人被捕<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1611575\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1611575</a>"},{"pid":"a56eb77d628886f4f092bbfa42e3c82a3b5da6de","tid":1611564,"uid":183971,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T04:02:44.000Z","msg":"豬咀其實都會過期"},{"pid":"46e42edb32687f5b6429f209551216d9952ec76f","tid":1611564,"uid":137009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T04:02:53.000Z","msg":"可唔可以幫手推下"},{"pid":"5b3ee058026a3466f53b345da8577c281c378eba","tid":1611564,"uid":137009,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a56eb77d628886f4f092bbfa42e3c82a3b5da6de","tid":1611564,"uid":183971,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T04:02:44.000Z","msg":"豬咀其實都會過期"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T04:03:42.000Z","msg":"對家大把貨<br />\n夠期咪換過新嫁囉"},{"pid":"bbb14c1f4ce02e5b23bea9ea384c6e3a44a4c9a5","tid":1611564,"uid":31974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T04:05:03.000Z","msg":"睇風向<br />\n